title: Ep. - 218 - DALLAS HOUSEWIVES REUNION, THE BACHELOR AND VANDERPUMP RULES PREMIERES
description:
D’Andra Simmons answers a speed round of questions about this season on Real Housewives of Dallas on Bravo, including whether she believes her mother spent all the money in her trust. 

 

Comedian and Betches podcast host Jared Freid helps Kate review the season premiere of The Bachelor on ABC. 

 

AOL Entertainment Managing Editor Gibson Johns helps Kate review the season premiere of Vanderpump Rules on Bravo.
